colours <- c("#0000ff", "#000000", "#ff0000")

plot_ly(tt, 
    x = ~logFC, 
    y = ~-log10(P.Value),
    color = ~ Group,  
    text = ~ Symbol,
    hoverinfo = "x+y+text",
